  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion1:Body": "<article><p>The information gathered can include but is not limited to:</p>\n            <p><strong>Contactable information:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Your contact details, which may include your parental or personal address</li>\n                <li>Links to social media accounts</li>\n                <li>Any consent that is provided in any opt-in options.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p><strong>Personal information:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Name, date of birth</li>\n                <li>Professional contact details</li>\n                <li>Links to businesses and other third parties</li>\n                <li>Educational history (with this or other universities)</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p><strong>Financial information:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Your bank account number, name, and sort code for processing orders</li>\n                <li>Details of your financial transactions with the university</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p><strong>Interactions with the university:</strong></p>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Your website activity and interaction with emails sent.</li>\n                <li>Your education at the University</li>\n                <li>Volunteering activity for the University</li>\n                <li>Prizes and awards achieved whilst attending university events and activities.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>We may also collect, store and use &ldquo;special categories&rdquo; of more sensitive information, but only with your consent and when it is relevant to your relationship with the College.</p></article>",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion1:Header": "What information will you store?",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion2:Body": "<article><p>Much of the information that we hold is obtained directly from you. The ways we collect your data directly including through contact detail update forms, donation forms, event registrations and in person. If you are a student, or studied at the University, some of your data can be transferred from your student record to the universitys alumni database. Personal data collected from you by other University departments may also be used for Advancement purposes, depending on the circumstances under which it is collected.</p></article>",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion2:Header": "How is the information collected?",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion3:Body": "<article><p>The university is committed to securing your data, in line with the universitys Data Protection policies and relevant legislation. Personal data is held on secure servers and these servers are accessed only by authorised personnel. In the event of a data breach, we will notify you and any applicable regulator, where we are legally obliged.</p></article>",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion3:Header": "Is my information secure?",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion4:Body": "<article><p>Only the key personal information will be kept where necessary or until the purpose for collection of the data has been fulfilled.</p></article>",
  "BiometricRegistration:Accordion4:Header": "How long will you store my information?",
