  "PublishedOnImportEmailContent": "                 <p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.63636363636364; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); margin-top: 10pt; margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0 0 12pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">Please log on to your electronic document portal as soon as possible. You have an important new document to view and download.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding: 0 0 12pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">If you are using a portal for the first time you need to complete </span><a href=\"https://dcwstudent.othm.org.uk/registration\" style=\"text-decoration: none\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(5, 99, 193, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">registration</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\"> providing your </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">Email ID</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">, </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">Date of Birth</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\"> and OTHM 9 digits unique </span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">Learner Registration Number (LRN).</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">If you enter a different Email ID, incorrect Date of Birth and LRN which does not match our record the system will reject your registration and deny access to the portal.&nbsp; If you do not know your LRN, please check the learner registration confirmation email which you received at the time of registration with us.&nbsp; You can also contact your OTHM Study Centre who got a copy of the email.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt\">The electronic documents meet regulatory requirements and are verifiable and accessible instantly by scanning QR code with a smartphone. Your electronic documents are provided with no extra cost. If you still require a printed copy you need to order using the portal.&nbsp; An additional cost and courier fees will apply.&nbsp; You can also seek assistance from your OTHM Study Centre.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0; text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial\">Yours sincerely</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0; text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0; text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">eCertification Team</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0; text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial\">OTHM Qualifications</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0; text-align: justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt\">United Kingdom&nbsp;</span></p>                 ",
